title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 4 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Nov 4 2022
description:
Wisconsin Senator Ron Johnson joins Clay and Buck to give us an update on his race to keep his seat. Biden lies again about the economy. Kari Lake unleashes searing Hillary Clinton joke. Clay predicts Lake will be the GOP VP nominee in 2024. Friend and radio show host Jesse Kelly hangs with C&B, makes midterm predictions. C&B close out the show talking with AZ congressional candidate Eli Crane.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
